def my_bar(values, labels):
    ax = plt.axes()
    ax.bar(range(len(values)),values)
    ax.set_xticks(np.array(range(len(values)))+0.4)
    ax.set_xticklabels(labels);

def list_from_df_series(df, series_names):
    els = []
    for col in series_names:
        els.extend(df[col])
    return els
 
all_tags = list_from_df_series(train, ["Tag1", "Tag2", "Tag3", "Tag4", "Tag5"])

In [33]:
 
def density(x, y, bins=100, xlim=None):
    if xlim is not None:
        data = [(a,b) for a,b in zip (x,y) if xlim[0]<=a<=xlim[1]]
        x = [d[0] for d in data]
        y = [d[1] for d in data]
    heatmap, xedges, yedges = np.histogram2d(y, x, bins=bins)
    extent = [yedges[0], yedges[-1], xedges[0], xedges[-1]]
    width = xedges[-1]-xedges[0]
    height = yedges[-1]-yedges[0]
    plt.imshow(heatmap, extent=extent, aspect=height/width, origin="lower")
 
density(body_length, open_prob, xlim=[0, 1000], bins=200)
